# Changelog

## Season 0 Beta

### 2026-05-06 — Initial Beta Setup

- **Added**: Core server infrastructure and plugin configuration
- **Added**: Town Hall layout and initial NPC placements
- **Added**: Starter job system (Miner, Farmer, Builder, Merchant, Industrialist, Civil Service)
- **Added**: Public contracts board (v0.1) with basic material contracts
- **Added**: Market district plot layout and initial shop assignments
- **Added**: Resource world (resets weekly)
- **Added**: Skill tree framework (passive buffs active, major unlocks in progress)
- **Added**: Land claim system with starter and commercial zones
- **Added**: Basic law system (fines, jail time)
- **Balance**: Starter job pay rates set at beta values — subject to adjustment
- **Notes**: Server IP and whitelist to be announced. Economy values are being observed and will be adjusted based on testing data.

---

*More updates will appear here as beta progresses.*

